title: Moorings
description: Moorings follows 23-year old Anne Holloway as she journeys up to a small, Alaskan fishing town to find her biological father. Instead of finding what she came looking for, Anne realizes the past can never be untangled from people's memories, and damage from oil spilled under the surface never completey dissolves. Still, by making the journey, Anne discovers her true identity can be found within.
author: Nancy Slavin
